Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Words of ancient times...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,475)\blur0.3\move(3100,650,1613,650,0,500)\t(3500,4000,\4a&HFF&)}Word Chain Game Under the Heated Table
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,People say each one of them had magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Those words went on endlessly, connecting to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest fortifying the barrier around this society using them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the word chain game, aren't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you got that after {\i1}that{\i0} explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be exaggerating if I called the deep bond between Master and me "one in body and soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Which leads us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Wicked Eye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"...is all-powerful."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Uriel."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Louis XIII."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stone."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"The deadly Wicked Eye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"...was sealed"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"...with a lost artifact."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it real!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Death would come get Master if she wasn't at least this witty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us continue with "the locked up castle of darkness."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Royal Warrant."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whetstone."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How cowardly of you to keep ending them with "shi," Nibutani!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to hear that from {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of cowardice up to the top of your fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts like death!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi... shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, five seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't miss the Wicked Eye calling Death's powers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As if that TV-promo-like answer is a legit answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan on taking over a TV station to make that show?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trembling with fear of death thinking about that plan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to advance the plan by advancing into the station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're irritating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Antiquity."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Edelweiß."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sushi."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A-As I thought, you are of the light element.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the enemy of the Wicked Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what a gutless girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's "shi!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi... shi shi shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, five seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi... shi shi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"D-Don't miss the Wicked Eye escaped death!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let that rest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And shouldn't it be "{\i1}escaping{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,T-T... T-This is all your fault anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the ancient word "shi" more often than you'd ever find it in the Infinite Corridor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.76,Default,,0,320,0,,She's really our enemy, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Another peaceful day.
